          TRANSLATION THAT<br /> FOLLOWS SOFTWARE<br /> BEST PRACTICES
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0">
        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-glossia-pink border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke="currentColor"
