            TRANSLATIONS ARE AUTOMATICALLY GENERATED AND TESTED WITH EVERY COMMIT, ENSURING QUALITY AND CONSISTENCY.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-black border-4 border-l-0 border-black p-8">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-glossia-pink border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center">
