            ALL TRANSLATIONS GO THROUGH AN AUTOMATED MERGE QUEUE, ENSURING YOUR MAIN BRANCH STAYS STABLE.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-l-0 border-black p-8">
